## Success Metrics

1. Reduce time to create proposal/order from ~30 min to <5 min
2. Eliminate equipment double-booking incidents
3. Customer lookup in <10 seconds (vs manual file search)
4. Single source of truth for all business data

## Constraints

- Budget: $15,000 (noted in case study)
- Must support growth to 10-15 employees
- Must be accessible to non-technical staff (Martha, technicians)

## MVP Deliverables

1. Customer CRUD with search
2. Equipment CRUD with status tracking
3. Order/Proposal/Invoice creation with line items
4. Equipment reservation calendar with conflict prevention
5. Basic dashboard with today's view

